snippet.title: Full Throttle ZX Spectrum
snippet.description:
From the man who brought you Deathchase comes......a bog-standard motorbike racing game.....oh the shame!

Okay I probably shouldn't knock the game too much but it badly flickers and its annoying that even with the slightest of touches you lose all of your speed.  And simply put it is nowhere near as good as Deathchase.
